      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open-checkbook policy. A buyer can expect a collector-grade vehicle that requires nothing but a new owner to appreciate its exceptional preservation.",
