      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS to deliver a surgical throttle response. Power is managed via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a functional M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor-pan stress fractures. Suspension remains composed with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampening. This example represents a strong driver-quality vehicle with a healthy compression profile and a recently serviced cooling system, ideal for the purist seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
